descriptionHtml:
1.Connected to your mobile phone by bluetooth4.0，your weight data, health status and BMI value calculated by your weight and height will display on your app. We care your figure with daily record every minutes.

3.Holding baby mode: you can measure your baby's weight accurately with only four simple steps.
